  "instructions": [
    "preheat the grill to 400\t30c (200\u000f) on the binchotan charcoal.",
    "brush the cod fillet with olive oil and season with fajita seasoning, salt and black pepper.",
    "place the cod fillet on the grill and cook for 4 minutes per side.",
    "meanwhile, slice the onion and garlic and saut\u000639 in butter until softened.",
    "add the lemon juice and plain yogurt to the onion and garlic mixture and stir to combine.",
    "add the chopped fresh dill to the onion and garlic mixture and stir to combine.",
    "once the cod is cooked, place it on a plate and top with the onion and garlic mixture.",
    "serve the cod with baby potatoes on the side, garnished with additional fresh dill if desired.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
